Elmo McElroy (Jackson) is a streetwise American master chemist who heads to England to sell his special new formula - a powerful, blue concoction guaranteed to take you to \&#039;the 51st state.
\&#039;McElroy\&#039;s new product delivers a feeling 51 times more powerful than any thrill, any pleasure, any high in history. 
But his plans for a quick, profitable score go comically awry when he gets stuck in Liverpool with an unlikely escort (Carlyle) and his ex-girlfriend (Mortimer) and becomes entangled in a bizarre web of double-dealing and double-crosses.
